description:
v4W.ENko - "PS07-3D01" plant is  related to the "PS-07-Voronoi-Flow_Radials" pattern experiment [HEN#486649] when the logic makes the next evolution`s cycle. The "plants" are generated from the transformation of the same "Voronoi diagram" flow demonstrated in 2d during the "PS-07-Voronoi-Flow_Radials" by adding the 3-d dimension. The custom utility transforms the standard pattern into the special plant.


Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 181 frames.
